// Translation format :
// [Japanese text] : [Translation text] : [Actual meaning/ Direct Translation]

回復の粉 : Potion : Powder of recovery
体力を小回復します : Small HP recovery : Physical strength is recovered(small.
回復ラクリマ : Potion+ : Recovery {rakurima}
体力を中回復します: Medium HP recovery : Physical strength is recovered(medium)
回復ディアマ : Potion++ : Recovery {deiama}
体力を全回復します : Full HP recovery : All physical strength is recovered
共復の粉 : HiPotion :
エリア内の味方全員の体力を小回復します : Allies around player recover some HP : All allies recover their strength in a small area
共復ラクリマ : HiPotion+ :
エリア内の味方全員の体力を中回復します : Allies around player recover medium HP : Restores the physical strength of all the allies in the area
共復ディアマ :HiPotion++ :
エリア内の味方全員の体力を全回復します : Allies around player recover all HP : Physical strength in the area all allies is recovered(full)
魔力の粉 : Ether : Powder of magic
魔力を全回復します : Small MP recovery : restore magic
魔力ラクリマ : Ether+ 
魔力を全回復し、３秒間魔力が減少しません : Medium MP recovery. MP freezes for 3 sec. : Magic is recovered, and all magic doesn't decrease for three seconds.
魔力ディアマ : Ether++
魔力を全回復し、５秒間魔力が減少しません : High MP recovery. MP freezes for 5 sec. :Magic is recovered, and all magic doesn't decrease for five seconds.
返魂ラクリマ : Phoenix Down
戦闘不能になったパートナーが
その場で体力が半分回復し復活します : Revives KO'd character with 1/2 HP : Revived on the spot to recover half of their strength
返魂ディアマ : Mega Phoenix
戦闘不能になったパートナーが
その場で体力が全回復し復活します : Revives KO with full HP  : Revived on the spot to recover all of their strength
救命ラクリマ : Phoenix Pin
プレイヤーが戦闘不能になると
その場で体力が半分回復し自動復活します : Auto revive KO'd character with 1/2 HP : Auto revived on the spot to recover half of their strength
救命ディアマ : Phoenix Pin+
プレイヤーが戦闘不能になると : : When the player cannot battle
その場で体力が全回復し自動復活します : Auto revive KO with full HP : The physical strength all recovers at that place and revives automatically
ソレム膏 : Remedy : Solem ointment
状態異常を回復します : Cure abnormal status : Restores abnormal status
リターンパウダー : Recall : Return Powder
ベースキャンプに一瞬で戻ります : Return to base : Return immediately to the base camp
エキサイトビット
ボルテージゲージを小回復します : : Voltage gauge is recovered(small)
剛腕ラクリマ : Strength Up
一定時間攻撃を強化します : Atk Pwr temp. increased : The attack is strengthened during the fixed time.
剛腕ディアマ : Strength Up+
一定時間攻撃を大きく強化します : Atk Pwr temp. increased a lot : The attack is greatly strengthened during the fixed time.
硬身ラクリマ : Defense Up
一定時間防御を強化します : Def temp. increased : The defense is strengthened during the fixed time.
硬身ディアマ : Defense Up+
一定時間防御を大きく強化します : Def temp. increased a lot : The defense is greatly strengthened during the fixed time.